1 Geh8 4 Jit8
Kim-ku3: “Ia5-sou ka7 i kong2, ... u7 sin3 e5 lang5 tak8-hang7 long2 oe7.” (Ma2-kho2 9:23)
1). Pun2-kho3 na7 beh li7-iong7 cho3 khui-hoe7 le2-pai3, m7-thang kong2 “beh kong2 kou3-su7”, in-ui7 hak8-seng oe7 koan3-si3, siunn7 kong2 lai5 le2-pai3 si7 thiann kou3-su7. Tioh8 chai chit e5 kou3-su7 si7 pang-chan7 li2 kong2 to7-li2 na7-tiann7, tioh8 ka-ki7 chou-chit ho2-ho2 e5 ji5-tong5 soat-kau3.
2). Pun2-kho3 e5 kim-ku3 si7 “U7 sin3 e5 lang5 tak8-hang7 long2 oe7,” chit e5 “tak8-hang7 khah ho2 tioh8 chi2-to7 hak8-seng ti7 ui7 Chu2 cho3 kang e5 kang-chok siong7.” Pun2-kou3-su7 si7 li7-iong7 Lou7-tek Ma2-teng e5 kau3-hoe7 kek-beng7 seng5-kong.
Lou7-tek Ma2-teng si7 chit8 e5 chin iong2-kam2 e5 lang5. I tui3 sin3-kho3 Siong7-te3 oan5-seng5 se3-kai3 choe3 iau3-kin2 e5 su7! 1517 ni5, tu2 tui3 chim-ma2 sng3-khi2 442 ni5, ti7 Tek-kok u7 lang5 tui3 Lo5-ma2 lai5 teh boe7 sia3-choe7-kng3, si7 Hoat-ong5 chhe i lai5 e5, i chheng7 chin-sui2 e5 sann hou7 chin choe7 lang5 giah8 ki5-a2 ka7 i hoan-geng5. I chiu7 tui3 cheng3-lang5 kong2: “Li2 khoann3 thian-kok e5 mng5 khui lah. Kin-a2-jit8 lin2 na7 m7 jip8 thian-kok beh theng3-hau7 sim2-mih8 si5! Bu5-ti e5 bin5-chiong3 ah! Chainn2-iunn7 hiah nih nge7-sim! Lin2 chi2-u7 chhut 12 khou boe2 chit8-tiunn sia3-choe7-kng3, chiu7 oe7 kiu3 lin2 lau7-pe7 tui3 te7-gak8 chhut-lai5. Lin2 kiam2 hiah-nih put-hau3, bo5 beh kiu3 ti7 te7-gak8 teh siu7-khou2 e5 lau7-pe7? Goa2 ka7 lin2 kong2 ti7 choe3-au7 e5 sim2-phoann3 e5 si5, goa2 oe7 tit-kiu3, chong2-si7 lin2 boe7 tit-kiu3!....Sia3-choe7-kng3 chhun bo5 loa7-che7 la3, thian-kok e5 mng5 tit beh koainn khi2-lai5 lah, tann tioh8 koann2-kin2 lai5 be2.”
Lou7-tek Ma2-teng thiann chit-khoan2 e5 oe7, hui-siong5 siu7-khi3. Sim2-mih8 thian-kok eng7 chinn5 oe7 boe2-tit! Chi2-u7 siunn7 beh than3-chinn5 bo5 chit8-sut-sut-a2 jiat8-sim beh kiu3 lang5 e5 leng5-hun5! Lou7-tek Ma2-teng siunn7 kau3 hit si5 Kau3-hong5 cho3-thau5 e5 kau3-hoe7 hiah-nih hu2-pai7, bo5 than3 Seng3-keng, bo5 to7-li2, chit-khoan2 eng-kai tioh8 kai2. Chong2-si7 Kau3-hong5 e5 se3-lek8 chin toa7, i2-cheng5 kui2-na7 lang5 ia7 ui7-tioh8 ai3 kai2 m7-tioh8 khi3 e5 kau3-hoe7, soa3 hou7 Kau3-hong5 chhu2 si2-heng5.
Chong2-si7 iong2-kam2, ui7-tioh8 Siong7-te3 e5 kau3-hoe7 jiat8-sim e5 Ma2-teng, long2 bo5 kiann-hiann5, sin3-kho3 Siong7-te3, lang5 boe7-oe7, Siong7-te3 tak8-hang7 long2 oe7. I chiu7 sin3-kho3 Siong7-te3 sia2 95 tiau5 e5 i3-kian3-su, tah ti7 kau3-hoe7 e5 mng5-nih. Bo5 phah-sng3 koe3 bo5 2 le2-pai3 choan5 Tek-kok long2 chai chit e5 tai7-chi3, bo5 4 le2-pai3 thoan5 kau3 choan5 se3-kai3, kau3-hoe7 kai2-kek e5 hoe2 tui3 an2-ni tiam2-tioh8!
Koh bo5 ku2 tui3 Kau3-hong5-thiann u7 beng7-leng7 lai5 kio3 Ma2-teng tioh8 ti7 60 jit8-lai7 chhu2-siau te7 41 tiau5, na7 bo5 beh liah8-khi3 Kau3-hong5 hia teng7 choe7, chit e5 te7 41 tiau5 chiu7 si7 kong2 an2-ni, “Beh be2 bo5 lou7-eng7 e5 sia3-choe7-kng3, m7-tat8-tioh8 chiong hiah e5 chinn5 chin2-che3 song3-hiong lang5 khah u7 li7-ek.” Lou7-tek Ma2-teng chai i sou2 sia2 e5 bo5 ui5-keh Siong7-te3, chiu7 koat-teng7 m7 chhu2-siau, soah ti7 chin choe7 lang5 e5 bin7-cheng5 sio hit tiunn beng7-leng7-su, khoann3 e5 lang5 long2 kam2-sim i e5 iong2-kam2, chhut toa7-siann hang2-hoah.
Au7-lai5 i tu2-tioh8 chin choe7 e5 gui5-hiam2 chong2-si7 long2 sin3-kho3 Siong7-te3 lai5 tek-seng3. I kong2, “Siat-su2 Mou5-kui2 chhin-chhiunn7 chhu3-hia7 hiah-nih choe7, goa2 ia7 bo5 kiann i.”
Tui3 Lou7-tek Ma2-teng e5 sin3-sim, kau3-hoe7 kai2-kek chiu7 seng5-kong. Kau3-hoe7 koh tit-tioh8 chu7-iu5 kap chin-li2, than3 Seng3-keng e5 ka3-si7, thoan5 si3-chiann3 e5 to7-li2.
Kin-a2-jit8 e5 kim-ku3 ka7 lan2 kong2, “Sin3 e5 lang5 tak8-hang7 long2 oe7” sit8-chai7 u7-iann2! Sio2 peng5-iu2, lin2 na7 tu2-tioh8 khun3-lan5 e5 su7, m7-thang sit-chi3, tioh8 eng7 sin3-sim iong2-kam2 lai5 choe3, lin2 chiu7 iu5-goan5 beh cho3 ui2-tai7 e5 su7-giap8. (T. T. T.)
1 Geh8 11 Jit8
Kim-ku3: Li2 iau2 khiam3 chit8 hang7; tioh8 khi3 boe7 li2 hoan7 sou2 u7 e5, lai5 hou7 song3-hiong lang5 ... koh lai5 toe3 goa2. (Ma2-kho2 10:21)
(Iau3-chi2) Ho2-giah8 e5 chheng-lian5 chainn2-iunn7 boe7 thang toe3 Ia5-sou. I sou2 u7 e5 chai5-san2, chai5-leng5 ... chou2-tong3 i. Ti7 se3-kan bo5 chit8-hang7 pi2 toe3 Ia5-sou lai5 oah8 khah iau3-kin2.
(Lau7-su e5 chun2-pi7)
Chhiann2 chun2-pi7: 1) Ui7-tioh8 u7 ----chai5-leng5, kian7-khong, chai5-san2 teng2 ---- boe7 thang toe3 Chu2 Ia5-sou e5 sit8-le7.
2) Ui7-tioh8 bo5, oe7-thang jip8 Siong7-te3 kok e5 lang5 e5 sit8-le7.
3) Sui-jian5 u7, chong2-si7 ui7 Ia5-sou hi-seng it-chhe3, koe3 ui2-tai7 e5 seng-oah8 e5 sit8-le7.
(Kou3-su7)
Chha-put-to 1600 ni5 cheng5, ti7 Ai-kip8 kok u7 chit8 lang5, lang5 chheng i cho3 seng3-chia2 e5 An-to7-ni2. An-to7-ni2 si7 chhut-si3 ti7 chin ho2-giah8 e5 lang5 e5 chhu3. Tak8-jit8 na7 ai3 chiah8 sim2-mih8 chiu7 u7 sim2-mih8, ai3 sim2-mih8 to7 u7 sim2-mih8, chin chu7-iu5 bo5 khiam3-khoeh teh koe3 jit8. Chong2-si7 18 hoe3 e5 si5 i e5 pa-pa, ma-ma long2 li7-khui se3-kan, sou2-i2 kap sio2-moe7 2 lang5 sann-kap koe3 jit8.
U7 chit8 jit8 thak8 Seng3-keng e5 si5, thak8 tioh8 “Li2 iau2 khiam3 chit8 hang7; tioh8 khi3 boe7 li2 hoan7 sou2 u7 e5, lai5 hou7 song3-hiong lang5 ...... siunn7 kong2 goa2 na7 bo5 chiau3 Ia5-sou sou2 kong2 e5 boe7-eng7-tit, tui3 an2-ni chiong sou2 u7 e5 chai5-san2 be7-be7 khi3, ia7 sio2-moe7 kau-tai3 iau2 chit8 e5 sin3-tou5 e5 ka-teng5, chiong sou2 be7 e5 chinn5 lai5 pun hou7 che7-che7 song3-hiong lang5. I ka-ki7 long2 bo5 poann3-hang7 lah, sou2-i2 i chiu7 khi3 chhau2-te7 sou2-chai7, khai-si2 cho3 kang, ia7 ki5-to2 thak8 Seng3-keng. Keng-koe3 10 ni5, 20 ni5, chin che7 lang5 lai5 cho3 i e5 hak8-seng, koe3 tioh8 sui-jian5 san3-hiong, chong2-si7 chin khoai3-lok8 ki5-to2 e5 seng-oah8. Hit tiong-kan i sou2 toa3 e5 si3-ui5 long2 ui7-tioh8 hiah e5 hak8-seng e5 chhau2-liau5 chiann5 cho3 chat8-thong2-thong2. In tai7-ke sann-kap ki5-to2, kim3-chiah8, sann-kap ka3-si7.
Au7-lai5 i thiann-tioh8 A-lek8-san-tai7 che7-che7 sin3-tou5 ui7-tioh8 Ia5-sou e5 mia5 hou7 lang5 pek-hai7, sou2-i2 i ia7 ai3 ui7-tioh8 toe3 Ia5-sou lai5 hi-seng, chiu7 khi3 A-lek8-san-tai7 e5 sou2-chai7. Chong2-si7 long2 bo5 1 lang5 beh hai7 i, lian7 hong5-te3 ia7 kong2 ai3 beh cho3 i e5 hak8-seng lai5 chhoe7 i, sou2-i2 i chiu7 ho2-tann2 kong2, “m7-thang khoa-khau2 se3-kan e5 koan5-lek8, tioh8 chun2 Ia5-sou cho3 eng2-oan2 e5 ong5, kiann5 cheng3-gi7 pang-chan7 song3-hiong lang5.” I ti7 105 hoe3 chiah to3-tng2 khi3 thian-kok.
Chit e5 An-to7-ni2 ui7 Chu2 pang3-sak it-chhe3, chong2-si7 tit-tioh8 kui2-na7 pah poe7 po2-kui3 e5 mih8. I siu7 chun-chong5 cho3 siu-to7-inn7 (Sin5-hak8-inn7) e5 si2-chou2. (T. H. C.)
