Kim-ku3: Goa2 e5 chhu3 beh chheng-choe3 ki5-to2 e5 chhu3, na7-si7 lin2 chiah e5 hou7 i choe3 chhat8-siu7. (Ma2-thai3 21:13)
U7 chit8 e5 cha-bou2 gin2-na2 kio3 choe3 A-hiong, toa3 ti7 chit8 e5 siann5-chhi7, ma-ma u7 sang3 i khi3 in e5 kau3-hoe7 e5 iu3-ti7-hng5 thak8-chheh, i chin ai3 chhiunn3 chit8-te3 “chian-chian sou2-chia2 si5-si5-sou5” e5 koa, ia7 chin e7 ki3-tit lau7-su kong2 sin-khu sann-khou3 put-si5 tioh8 ai3 chin chheng-khi3 chiu7 khah boe7 phoa3-pinn7, ia7 chhu3-nih e5 pang5-keng kheh-thiann, lai7-goa7-tiann5 tioh8 ai3 cheng2-li2 chheng-kiat chiu7 khah kian7-khong. A-hiong sui-jian5 se3-han3, ti7 chhu3-nih chin gau5 sau3-te7 chhit thang-a2, ia7 chin chheng-khi3-siunn3, put-si5 khoann3-tioh8 chin kou2-chui2. Chit e5 A-hiong 10 hoe3 e5 si5 ui7-tioh8 pa-pa e5 su7-giap8, chiu7 kap pe7-bu2 poann khi3 ti7 chit8 e5 chng-kha khia7-khi2.
Le2-pai3-jit8 u7 khi3 Chu2-jit8-oh8, i kau3 le2-pai3-tng5, gin2-na2 bo5 loa7 che7, sio2-chhu3 koainn leh, le2-pai3-tng5 chin ak-chak, po-le5-thang chin che7 hong-poe-soa, ti-tu-si khan kau3 chin-che7, pai3-tng5 e5 goa7-khau2 hoat chin che7 chhau2, khoann3-tioh8 kann-na2 chhin-chhiunn7 choa5 bih ti7 hia, chin m7 koan3-si3, u7 chit8 jit8 i tui3 le2-pai3-tng5 keng-koe3 khoann3-tioh8 pai3-tng5 lai7 u7 lang5 ti7 hia teh kong2-oe7, A-hiong chit8 e7 jip8-khi3 khoann3, u7 kui2-na7 e5 choh-sit lang5, chiong in e5 chhek-a2 kap thou5-tau7 khng3 ti7 pai3-tng5 lai7, A-hiong chin kan-khou2-sim, tng2-khi3 i chiu7 ki5-to2 Siong7-te3 kong2, “Siong7-te3 ah, goa2 khi3 Chu2-jit8-oh8 khoann3-tioh8 le2-pai3-tng5 ak-chak chin m7 koan3-si3, kin-a2-jit8 koh khoann3-tioh8 lang5 khng3 mih8 ti7 hia goa2 khoann3 tioh8 sim chin kan-khou2, Siong7-te3, Li2 tek-khak si7 chin bo5 hoann-hi2, in-ui7 si7 li2 e5 tian7, goa2 chin ai3 chit keng pai3-tng5 e7-thang chhin-chhiunn7 goa2 i2-cheng5 khi3 hit keng chin chheng-khi3, goa2 si7 chit8 e5 gin2-na2 goa2 tu2-a2 lai5 bo5 phoann7, kiu5 Li2 hou7 goa2 u7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 peng5-iu2 goa2 beh chio in lai5 chheng-sau3.”
A-hiong u7 ke3-siok8 khi3 thak8 Chu2-jit8-oh8, ia7 ke3-siok8 ki5-to2, ko2-jian5 2 geh8 jit8 au7 u7 che7-che7 Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 hak8-seng kap i choe3 chin-ho2 e5 peng5-iu2, ia7 chin thiann3 i, i chiu7 tui3 in kong2 i2-cheng5 khi3 e5 kau3-hoe7 chin chheng-khi3, chio peng5-iu2 ti7 pai3 6 e7-pou sann-kap chheng-sau3 pai3-tng5, kau3 pai3 6 e7-pou chiann5 10 e5 gin2-na2 u7 e5 toa3 sau3-chhiu2 u7 e5 toa3 toh-pou3, u7 e5 toa3 pun3-ki khi3 chheng-sau3, in-ui7 si7 gin2-na2 lang5, le2-pai3-tng5 hiah toa7 keng sau3 boe7 chheng-khi3, sou2-i2 chit8 nng7 le2-pai3 e5 tiong-kan hoe7-iu2 lai5 le2-pai3 ia7 bo5 sim2-mih8 kam2-kak, chong2-si7 kau3 1 geh8 jit8 au7 hit keng le2-pai3-tng5 e5 lai7-goa7 chiu7 pinn3 choe3 chin chheng-khi3, Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 lau7-su chin ki5-koai3, kann2 si7 tiong2-chip u7 chhiann2 lang5 lai5 sau3, in-ui7 au7 le2-pai3 beh Koh-oah8-cheh. Tiong2-chip ia7 ki5-koai3 kann2 si7 ui7-tioh8 Koh-oah8-cheh Chu2-jit8-oh8 e5 lau7-su u7 kio3 hak8-seng lai5 chheng-sau3, mng7 lai5 mng7 khi3 chiah chai si7 A-hiong kap kui2-ui7 peng5-iu2 lai5 chheng-sau3 e5. 
Tiong2-chip, lau7-su, hoe7-iu2 thiann-tioh8 ia7 chin hoann-hi2 ia7 chin kian3-siau3, hou7 pat8-ui7 lai5 e5 Chu2-jit8-oh8 hak8-seng e5 sou2 choe3 siu7 toa7 kam2-tong7, tu2-tu2 hit cha2-khi2 e5 le2-pai3 si7 Chu2 e5 siu7-lan7-chiu, sin5-hak8-inn7 phai3 lai5 e5 sin5-hak8-seng sou2 kong2 e5 to7-li2 chiu7-si7 Ia5-sou chheng-khi3 Seng3-tian7 e5 to7-li2, A-hiong e5 sou2 choe3 m7-na7 hit keng kau3-hoe7 chai, ia7 u7 thoan5 kau3 sin5-hak8-inn7, au7-lai5 chit keng pai3-tng5 put-si5 chin chheng-khi3, goa7-khau2-tiann5 ia7 cheng3-hoe khui kau3 chin sui2, choh-sit-lang5 khoann3-tioh8 hiah-nih chheng-khi3 ia7 m7-kann2 koh khng3 mih8, le2-pai3-jit8 bo5 lang5 phui3 pin-nng5-chiap, bo5 lang5 ti7 lai7-te2 ka7 gin2-na2 si-jio7 lah, A-hiong ia7 chhoa7 chin che7 hoe7-goa7 e5 sio2-peng5-iu2 siong5-siong5 lai5 chin sui2 e5 pai3-tng5 khoann3 hoe, le2-pai3-jit8 soa3 ai3 lai5 thak8 Chu2-jit8-oh8, ke-thinn chin che7 lang5. (C. I. L.)
